CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 25, 1957, pg. A17 reads: "AKA DEBS...who bowed in the 1957 Cotillion at the Penn-Sheraton Hotel, Saturday night, included these charmers: Patricia Mann, Sarah Blakey, Judith Matthews, Gayle Sands and Frances Pace."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six young women wearing light colored evening gowns, including Sara Blakey seated in center, and Frances Pace standing on right, posed in Penn Sheraton Hotel for the Alpha Kappa Alpha 1957 Cotillion
